<b>OUTBOUND</b><br />
Each outgoing message will be signed with a DKIM signatures.<br />
In your external DNS server, in <?= $domains[$count] ?> DNS zone, create a TXT record with the value provided for this domain.<br />
<br />
Click on OUTBOUND on each domain to copy its TXT record value.<br />
e.g.: <br />
v=DKIM1; p=MIGfMA0JO...PwdwIDAQAB
<br />
<br />
Optional: Input an ISP hostname or [ip.add.re.ss]:port where you want to forward all<br/>
your outgoing messages sent from each domain